arrayrange : rounding errors. When a sequence is generated with arrayrange (ex. arrayrange(-3,3,0.1)), the integer values -2, -1, 0,... are not true integers. Ex. 0==1.66e-16. This can result in errors, e.g. in statlib.py on line 423 (gausspdf)

